snippet: Gov. Scott Walker will meet with the Milwaukee County district attorney, who has been investigating the behavior of workers in his previous office, campaign officials said Friday.
lead_paragraph: Gov. Scott Walker will meet with the Milwaukee County district attorney, who has been investigating the behavior of workers in his previous office, campaign officials said Friday.
